                    Investment Bank
                
Markets
We serve our institutional investor clients by helping them to understand developments in global markets and offering execution and risk management tools across each major asset class.










 





 Credit
					 


				A globally coordinated platform providing sales and trading of cash, loans and derivative credit products, from investment grade, through high yield, emerging markets, distressed, and special situations.
				
			






 





 Equities Liquid Markets
					 


				Full service capabilities across content, issuance and execution for exchange traded and over the counter equities products.
				
			






 





 Macro
					 


				A consolidated platform for sales and trading of interest rate, foreign exchange and commodity derivative products.
				
			






 





 Prime Brokerage Services
					 


				Providing clients with a range of prime brokerage, execution, financing and clearing services.
				
			






 





 Structured and Financing Markets
					 


				Combining our capabilities across structured solutions and investment strategies to help institutional clients access the markets efficiently.
				
			







