BARCLAYS CAPITAL SECURITIES LIMITED
 


overview

Deposit Guarantee
Bank Identifiers



  


















Barclays Capital Securities Limited (Barclays Capital, BarCap) 
is a wholly owned subsidiary of Barclays Bank Plc and 
is part of the investment banking division of Barclays Bank. BARCLAYS CAPITAL SECURITIES LIMITED participates in deposit guarantee scheme of the United Kingdom. 
This scheme covers accounts up to 85 000 GBP per bank per depositor.  BARCLAYS CAPITAL SECURITIES LIMITED is a member of 
				Barclays (United Kingdom). BARCLAYS CAPITAL SECURITIES LIMITED is headquartered in London.




Address1 CHURCHILL PLACE, London, United KingdomPhone44 02076232323Fax44 02077736822 

Member of Group Barclays (United Kingdom)Start DateJuly 2016  
 


 

Deposit Guarantee85 000 GBP  
 


MFI IDGB0ECBM05468 

Company Number1929333 
 
 
 


